{"tid":567553,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人係過份自卑","createTime":"2018-02-21T03:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T12:27:41.000Z","uid":121394,"like":114,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"5c8ff7ee140e7b1ffbdf0093d82d2bb0d80a25ab","tid":567553,"uid":121394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T03:29:51.000Z","msg":"自卑到覺得自己毫無優點<br />\n乜都做唔好 無撚用<br />\n就連原先比自己差既人都已經超前咗自己<br />\n自己就一啲成就都無 又乜都唔敢踏出第一步<br />\n少少事可能係自己敏感咗 又將佢無限放大<br />\n有諗過自己係咪有depression 或者其他情緒病嗰啲又好似無咁嚴重<br />\n但就係日日係咁諗負面野 覺得自己點差點差比唔上人<br />\n係咪會逼死自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60567f87e2ebf89b1530a84e1182d9b42f58357","tid":567553,"uid":165482,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T03:31:34.000Z","msg":"比過分自信好<br />\n起碼無期望落空後的失望"},{"pid":"56d7341dcca768db9c049c808aec77053774cf17","tid":567553,"uid":14436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T03:33:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"768699f571a28c45222014038a4c15dd3078f723","tid":567553,"uid":121394,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c60567f87e2ebf89b1530a84e1182d9b42f58357","tid":567553,"uid":165482,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T03:31:34.000Z","msg":"比過分自信好<br />\n起碼無期望落空後的失望"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T03:35:20.000Z","msg":"都係既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但自信既話起碼唔會諗咁多負面野 想做就做<br />\n好羨慕啲人由內到外既自信 嗰個氣場同講出黎既野係唔同啲"},{"pid":"429bd5f8d8cf57f4a4b17e2cc1e4e0c66ee3180a","tid":567553,"uid":111872,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T03:41:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/21/114123_d248a69cae3825ff2ee33edd5f3f5bdc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F21%2F114123_d